Package org.blockchainnative.fabric

Class ChaincodeEventObservable

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.reactivex.Observable<Event<java.lang.String>>
      • org.blockchainnative.fabric.ChaincodeEventObservable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.reactivex.ObservableSource<Event<java.lang.String>>
    public class ChaincodeEventObservable
extends io.reactivex.Observable<Event<java.lang.String>>
    Represents an observable of Hyperledger Fabric chaincode events.

    An event listener is registered once the first Observer subscribes to it and unregistered when the last Observer is disposed.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    FabricEventInfo
